text: Hanaāejenauusade henee wauwau, nau hanaāenauhauthehaude hadāhewaunādaune nuu hayauhuhau. Wauhā hechauhauthethāhe hauauwuu hanaāasenaunade hanaāāedauwunaude hewauwaune, Yegauhu nauhauhaunee hadaugauchaudāe nau hadaugauchauchanee hedane, nau hadjāthaunauau hede hathāadavenuhunethee, nau henesenehehauau, nau jeneejavesahehauau, nau nanenauguhuhauau.
